TITLE: Chelsea takeover: Todd Boehly completes £4.25bn takeover as Roman Abramovich era ends
SUMMARY: The Todd Boehly-led consortium have completed a £4.25bn takeover of Chelsea, ending Roman Abramovich's 19-year ownership of the club.

TITLE: EU struggles to reach an agreement on Russian oil embargo as Hungary holds firm
SUMMARY: The talks are largely held up by Hungary, a major user of Russian oil and whose leader Viktor Orban is on friendly terms with Russia's Vladimir Putin.

SUMMARY: The revived luna token is already trading on exchanges. But its price is crashing.
